I have not done this, but have thought about it.  If I ever get around
to it, I intend to use a fairly heavy piece of steel for the surface
the machine mounts to.  Heavy being 1/4 or 3/8 inch with some studs or
something welded to  the bottom to act as rebar and mounting.  And
weld up a sheet metal form to cast the concrete into.  I would also
use some rebar in the concrete.  The sheet metal form ought to be
light enough to get into the basement.

